Cell[TextData[{
 "(i) Each element is twice the previous element. Generated by ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["t", "n"], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->"TraditionalForm",ExpressionUUID->
  "de16de84-56fa-4c0f-8e0e-894f89a2bd8d"],
 " = 3 ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    RowBox[{"(", "2", ")"}], 
    RowBox[{"n", " ", "-", " ", "1"}]], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->"TraditionalForm",ExpressionUUID->
  "ae34e65a-9808-4715-9055-eea45c05014e"],
 ". Next elements are 384, 768, and 1536.\n(ii) Each element is seven less \
than the previous term. Generated by ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["t", "n"], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->"TraditionalForm",ExpressionUUID->
  "9fa84fb7-0cc2-43d5-957d-242f65cc5bb4"],
 " = 15 - 7  (n - 1). Next elements are -34, -41, and -48.\n(iii) Each \
element is it\[CloseCurlyQuote]s position plus the the previous term. \
Generated by . Next elements are 57, 68, and 80.\n(iv) Each element is twelve \
times it\[CloseCurlyQuote]s position added with the previous term. Next \
elements are 1024, 1458, 2000.\n(v) Each element is the previous term times \
the position of the term to be found, minus the aforementioned position \
subtracted by one. Next elements are 362881, 3628801, 39916801."
}], "Text",
